        see:every example computed its own Voronoiology — each dataset crushed in parallel to its own reading world beside its data
        see:a population folds where lone kinds cannot — twelve boulders gang behind one pane while eight single kinds stay bare below the minimum
        see:the groves keep their own panes — three nested containers fold outermost into three cells and the crush never descends inside
        see:the model discovers order from the data — the gradient example reads depth as a numeric axis and pins its ten strata from one end anchor to the other
        see:the un-same folds as a group — five requests of varying value gang behind one representative where two ordinary cairns stay bare below the ordinary minimum
        see:the governor discovered the clades — twenty loose leaves overran the density budget so the crush escalated one level on its own and five genera each ganged behind a representative
        see:the model tells a fact from a spread — the flock orders by grade the spread that varies while stratum Miocene the value all twelve share rides as a shared fact
        see:a minority-but-loud trait keeps its count — the flock names vein and marks how many of the strata carry it not all so the claim the rep cannot count survives as a share
        see:sibling folds group by a shared property — Metrosideros and Kunzea land in one region while Olearia and Brachyglottis land in another so a secondary clade ropes the gangs the mainkey keeps apart
        see:a crowded fold drops nothing silently — the bare Relic pair carries more distinct facts than the four loudest the cap keeps so the model marks the crowded-out tail with an over count instead of letting it vanish
